<a href="policy.html">pol&iacute;tica</a> [Nota del 24 de enero:
bsd.tucows.com ha cerrado].

<p>
<li><font color="#009000"><strong>
<a href="http://www.ddj.com/documents/s=865/ddj0165a/">
Theo de Raadt, Todd Miller, Angelos Keromytis, Werner Losh,
and Jack Woehr at &quot;A Roundtable on BSD, Security, and
